src:
Hasil FP2 Moto2 Malaysia: Jorge Martin Memimpin
01 Nov 2019, 14:06 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Red Bull KTM Ajo, Jorge Martin, sukses mencatatkan waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas kedua (FP2) Moto2 Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Jumat (1/11/2019).
Pebalap Spanyol ini diikuti oleh pebalap ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team, Tetsuta Nagashima, di posisi kedua, dan pebalap Estrella Galicia 0,0 Marc VDS, Alex Marquez, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap Red Bull KTM Ajo lainnya, Brad Binder, dan pebalap Speed Up Racing, Jorge Navarro.
Berikut hasil FP2 Moto2 Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian Moto2 FP2 Results: Jorge Martin Leads
Nov 01 2019, 14:06 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Ajo KTM Red Bull rider, Jorge Martin, successfully recorded the fastest time in the second free practice session (FP2) Moto2 Malaysia at the Sepang Circuit on Friday (1/11/2019).
The Spanish rider was followed by ONEXOX TKKR SAG Team, Tetsuta Nagashima, in second place, and Estrella Galicia 0.0 Marc VDS, Alex Marquez, in third.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by other Red Bull KTM Ajo riders, Brad Binder, and Speed Up Racing racer, Jorge Navarro.
Following are the results of the 2012 Moto2 Malaysian FP9.
